descriptionHtml:
Caja-Ei, a follower, companion, and friend. Caja-Ei is an Argonian Assassin follower, ready to help any who require his services. Caja-Ei wears armor similar in design to the Shrouded Armor, in hopes to emulate the Shadowscales of old.
He wields an Orcish Dagger, an Elven bow, and Steel Arrows. He levels with the player, and can be found in Riverwood's Sleeping Giant Inn.
author: SebastianAB12
